---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const pageTitle = 'Terms of Service';
const pageDescription = 'Terms of Service for AgileTactix — online educational content and professional development resources for agile professionals.';
---

<BaseLayout title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription}>
  <style is:global>
    #main-nav {
      position: relative !important;
      background-color: rgb(3, 7, 18) !important;
    }
    #main-nav + div {
      display: none !important;
    }
  </style>

  <!-- Dark header section -->
  <section class="bg-black">
    <div class="max-w-[960px] mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 py-16 sm:py-20">
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight mb-4">
        Terms of Service
      </h1>
      <p class="text-gray-400 text-base">
        Effective Date: February 11, 2026<br />
        Last Updated: February 11, 2026
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-[960px] mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 py-16 sm:py-20 lg:py-24">

      <!-- Intro -->
      <div class="prose-content space-y-5 mb-14">
        <p>
          Welcome to AgileTactix. These Terms of Service ("Terms") govern your use of the website agiletactix.ai, our courses, digital products, email content, and related services (collectively, the "Services").
        </p>
        <p>
          AgileTactix is operated by LeanTech Creative, LLC ("AgileTactix," "we," "us," or "our"). By accessing or using the Services, you agree to these Terms. If you do not agree, please do not use the Services.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 1 -->
      <div class="mb-14">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-4">1. Services Overview</h2>
        <div class="prose-content space-y-5">
          <p>
            AgileTactix provides online educational content and professional development resources related to agile delivery practices, workflow automation, and AI-assisted team operations. Services may include: free and paid online courses, downloadable materials and templates, email newsletters and updates, and community and discussion features (when available). All Services are educational in nature.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 2 -->
      <div class="mb-14">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-4">2. Eligibility</h2>
        <div class="prose-content space-y-5">
          <p>
            You must be at least 18 years old to use our Services. By using the Services, you represent that you have the legal capacity to enter into this agreement.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 3 -->
      <div class="mb-14">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-4">3. Accounts & Access</h2>
        <div class="prose-content space-y-5">
          <p>
            Some Services require an email address or account access through a third-party platform (such as SamCart). You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your login credentials and for all activity occurring under your account. You agree to provide accurate information when registering and to update it as needed. We may suspend or terminate access if we reasonably believe your account is being shared, resold, or used in violation of these Terms.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 4 -->
      <div class="mb-14">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-4">4. Purchases & Payments</h2>
        <div class="prose-content space-y-5">
          <p>
            Payments are processed through third-party payment processors, including SamCart. By purchasing a product, you authorize the applicable charges to your selected payment method and agree to the payment processor's terms and policies. Prices are listed at the point of sale and may change at any time. All prices are in U.S. dollars unless stated otherwise.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 5 - Refund Policy (highlight box) -->
      <div class="mb-14">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-4">5. Refund Policy</h2>
        <div class="bg-[#f0f7ff] border-l-4 border-[#294bf3] rounded-r-lg p-6 sm:p-8">
          <div class="prose-content space-y-5">
            <p>
              We offer a <strong>30-day refund policy</strong> for digital course purchases. If a product is not a fit for your role or environment, you may request a refund within 30 days of purchase by contacting: <a href="mailto:danny@agiletactix.com" class="text-[#294bf3] underline">danny@agiletactix.com</a>.
            </p>
            <p>
              Refunds are issued to the original payment method. Processing time may vary depending on your financial institution. We reserve the right to deny refund requests in cases of abuse, repeated refund requests, or violations of these Terms.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 6 -->
      <div class="mb-14">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-4">6. Intellectual Property & License</h2>
        <div class="prose-content space-y-5">
          <p>
            All content provided through the Services — including videos, documents, templates, examples, branding, and written materials — is the property of AgileTactix and LeanTech Creative, LLC and is protected by copyright and intellectual property laws.
          </p>
          <p>
            When you purchase a product, you are granted a personal, non-exclusive, non-transferable license for your individual professional use only.
          </p>
          <p class="font-semibold text-[#1a1a1a]">You may NOT:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li>Share login credentials</li>
            <li>Redistribute course materials</li>
            <li>Upload content to public websites</li>
            <li>Resell or sublicense any material</li>
            <li>Train AI systems on course content</li>
            <li>Present the material as your own</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            Unauthorized use may result in termination of access and legal action.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 7 -->
      <div class="mb-14">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-4">7. Acceptable Use</h2>
        <div class="prose-content space-y-5">
          <p>
            You agree not to: violate applicable laws, attempt unauthorized access to systems, interfere with website functionality, impersonate others, or distribute harmful code or spam. We may suspend access for violations of these Terms.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 8 -->
      <div class="mb-14">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-4">8. Email Communications</h2>
        <div class="prose-content space-y-5">
          <p>
            By subscribing to our email list, you consent to receive educational emails, updates, and promotional messages. You may unsubscribe at any time using the link in any email. Email communications are delivered through third-party email providers.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 9 - Educational Disclaimer (amber highlight box) -->
      <div class="mb-14">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-4">9. Educational Disclaimer</h2>
        <div class="bg-amber-50 border-l-4 border-amber-400 rounded-r-lg p-6 sm:p-8">
          <div class="prose-content space-y-5">
            <p>
              Our Services are educational and informational only. We do not guarantee employment outcomes, promotions, salary increases, or business results. Your success depends on your background, effort, workplace environment, and external factors beyond our control.
            </p>
            <p>
              Nothing provided constitutes legal, financial, employment, or career counseling advice. References to third-party tools, platforms, or software are for instructional purposes only and do not imply affiliation or endorsement.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 10 -->
      <div class="mb-14">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-4">10. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <div class="prose-content space-y-5">
          <p>
            To the fullest extent permitted by law, AgileTactix and LeanTech Creative, LLC shall not be liable for indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from use of the Services. Our total liability for any claim shall not exceed the amount you paid for the product associated with the claim.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 11 -->
      <div class="mb-14">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-4">11. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <div class="prose-content space-y-5">
