            We may link to or integrate third-party services. We are not responsible for the availability, security, or policies of those services. Your use of third-party platforms is governed by their own terms.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 12 -->
      <div class="mb-14">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-4">12. Modifications</h2>
        <div class="prose-content space-y-5">
          <p>
            We may update these Terms at any time. Continued use of the Services after updates constitutes acceptance of the revised Terms.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 13 -->
      <div class="mb-14">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-4">13. Governing Law</h2>
        <div class="prose-content space-y-5">
          <p>
            These Terms are governed by the laws of the State of Florida, United States. Any disputes shall be resolved in the state or federal courts located in Florida.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 14 - Contact (highlight box) -->
      <div class="mb-14">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-4">14. Contact</h2>
        <div class="bg-[#f0f7ff] border-l-4 border-[#294bf3] rounded-r-lg p-6 sm:p-8">
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">Questions regarding these Terms may be sent to:</p>
          <p class="text-[#1a1a1a] font-semibold">AgileTactix</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Operated by LeanTech Creative, LLC</p>
          <p class="mt-2">
            <a href="mailto:danny@agiletactix.com" class="text-[#294bf3] underline">danny@agiletactix.com</a>
          </p>
          <p>
            <a href="https://agiletactix.ai" class="text-[#294bf3] underline">https://agiletactix.ai</a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
